456
00:37:11.000 --> 00:37:13.000
A lot of our opponents pray on emotion

457
00:37:13.000 --> 00:37:15.000
and to make wild statements

458
00:37:15.000 --> 00:37:18.000
and catastrophize about the state of the ocean

459
00:37:18.000 --> 00:37:20.000
