463
00:37:31.000 --> 00:37:33.000
or at a government level.

464
00:37:33.000 --> 00:37:35.000
On the other side, decisions made with emotion

465
00:37:35.000 --> 00:37:37.000
and bad information lead to bad outcomes

466
00:37:37.000 --> 00:37:40.000
and have unintended consequences to people.

467
00:37:41.000 --> 00:37:45.000
I think cameras on vessels are a good thing.

468
00:37:45.000 --> 00:37:48.000
I don't think the public should be available

469
00:37:48.000 --> 00:37:50.000
